list.name: Default
list.comment: .Added and created action to log in a user in Redux .Added functionality to decode the JSON webtoken .Created an is-empty method to check for null, undefined and empty JWT .Created and added a method called setAuthToken to add the token as default header in the axios requests to the REST api .Added a new action type in types.js called SET_CURRENT_USER
